# Daily Snapshot Cron Job
# Run daily at 6 AM UTC (adjust timezone as needed)
# 0 6 * * * cd /path/to/intention-growth-hub && npm run snapshots:daily

# Example for different timezones:
# 6 AM EST (UTC-5): 0 11 * * *
# 6 AM PST (UTC-8): 0 14 * * *
# 6 AM JST (UTC+9): 0 21 * * *

# To install this cron job:
# 1. Edit your crontab: crontab -e
# 2. Add the line above (uncommented)
# 3. Save and exit

# For Railway deployment, use Railway's cron feature:
# https://docs.railway.app/guides/cron-jobs

# For Vercel deployment, use Vercel Cron:
# https://vercel.com/docs/cron-jobs
